<div class="backgroundcolor">
  <div class="main_background text-center d-flex align-items-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="maintextsize">The London Massage</h1>
      <p class="secondtextsize">Expert massage, delivered to your door.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="about-section">
  <div class="about-wrapper">

    <div class="about-image">
      <%= cl_image_tag("diyqhv89wwxmes0okenq") %>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <h2 class="about-name">Tom Elsom</h2>
      <p class="about-role">Sports Therapist</p>

      <div class="about-divider"></div>

      <p class="about-text">
        I’ve spent the past 16 years helping people move without pain and perform at their best, from professional athletes and public figures to busy professionals balancing work and family life.
        <br><br>
        Now based in South London, I offer tailored, at-home treatments that fit seamlessly into your schedule. Every session is bespoke, combining hands-on therapy with practical movement advice where needed, so progress continues beyond the treatment room.
        <br><br>
        The focus is simple: sustainable results and long-term improvement.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
  <div class="container">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-center">Treatments</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center g-0">
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="card text-white">
            <div class="card-body theraputicbackgroundcolor">
              <%=cl_image_tag("therapeuticmassage_hemrkx", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Theraputic massage image")  %>
              <h3 class="card-title">Theraputic</h3>
              <h5><b>Restore balance. Reset the nervous system.</b></h5>
              <p>A deeply calming treatment designed to reduce accumulated stress and encourage full-body relaxation.</p>
              <h4 class="card-title">Benefits</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Calms the nervous system and reduces stress load</li>
                <li>Relieves muscular tension caused by daily strain</li>
                <li>Improves sleep quality</li>
                <li>Enhances mental clarity and emotional balance</li>
                <li>Promotes circulation and overall wellbeing</li>
                <li>Creates space for physical and psychological reset</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="card text-white">
            <div class="card-body deeptissuebackgroundcolor">
              <%=cl_image_tag("sports-massage-deep-tissue_ziu36h", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Deep tissue massage image")  %>
              <h3 class="card-title">Deep Tissue</h3>
              <h5><b>Targeted treatment for chronic tension.</b></h5>
              <p>A focused, slower-paced approach that works into deeper muscle layers to address persistent tightness and restriction.</p>
              <h4 class="card-title">Benefits</h4>
               <ul>
                 <li>Releases chronic muscular tension</li>
                 <li>Lowers blood pressure</li>
                 <li>Reduces chronic pain</li>
                 <li>Improves circulation</li>
                 <li>Breaks down adhesions and areas of restriction</li>
                 <li>Improves mobility and range of motion</li>
                 <li>Stress relief</li>
               <li>Supports recovery from repetitive strain</li>
               <li>Reduces long-standing neck, shoulder and lower back discomfort</li>
               <li>Enhances structural balance</li>
             </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body sportsremedialbackgroundcolor">
              <%=cl_image_tag("sprtmss_vaqdxe", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Sport massage image")  %>
              <h3 class="card-title">Sports & Remedial Massage</h3>
              <h5><b>Performance-driven, clinically informed treatment.</b></h5>
              <p>Designed for active and sedentary individuals who want to move better, recover faster and reduce injury risk.</p>
              <h4 class="card-title">Benefits</h4>
              <ul>
                 <li>Supports injury prevention strategies</li>
                 <li>Assists rehabilitation of minor strains and overuse issues</li>
                 <li>Reduces scar tissue and adhesions</li>
                 <li>Improves performance</li>
                 <li>Reduces pain</li>
                 <li>Identifies and addresses muscular imbalances</li>
                 <li>Improves movement efficiency and flexibility</li>
               <li>Releases tension</li>
               <li>Enhances pre-event preparation and post-event recovery</li>
               <li>Improves posture and functional movement patterns</li>
               <li>Reduces post-exercise soreness</li>
             </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="card text-white">
            <div class="card-body cuppingbackgroundcolor">
              <%=cl_image_tag("CuppingTherapy_uimjvb", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Cupping massage image")  %>
              <h3 class="card-title">Cupping</h3>
              <h5><b>Advanced myofascial decompression.</b></h5>
              <p>A specialised technique used to lift and decompress soft tissue, increasing local circulation and reducing fascial restriction.</p>
              <h4 class="card-title">Benefits</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Improves local blood flow</li>
                <li>Reduces deep muscular tightness</li>
                <li>Releases fascial restriction</li>
                <li>Supports recovery and tissue health</li>
                <li>Complements deep tissue and sports massage</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
